-- China to Halve Property Transaction Tax for Sole Residences to 1 Percent
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-09-29T13:29:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/china-to-halve-property-transaction-tax-for-sole-residences-to-1-percent.html
China will halve the real-estate
transaction tax for homebuyers who are purchasing a non-luxury
property that will be their sole residence, the Finance Ministry
said in statement on its website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Winnie Zhu in Shanghai at 
